{"word":"G2692 - καταστροφή - katastrophḗ - kat-as-trof-ay' - Overthrow","slug":"G2692","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταστροφή</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>katastrophḗ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kat-as-trof-ay'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Overthrow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>καταστροφή</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Katastrophe</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>kat-as-trof-ay'</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> overthrow, destruction </p> <p class='li520'><b>a.</b> of cities </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> metaph. of the extinction of a spirit of consecration </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G2690\">G2690</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 18:55,1 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Noun Feminine <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G2690\">G2690</a>; an <i>overturn</i> (catastrophe) that is <i>demolition</i>; figuratively <b><i>apostasy</i></b>: - overthrow subverting. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1294\">G1294</a>, <a href=\"#/G1994\">G1994</a>, <a href=\"#/G1995\">G1995</a>, <a href=\"#/G2690\">G2690</a>, <a href=\"#/G3344\">G3344</a>, <a href=\"#/G390\">G390</a>, <a href=\"#/G391\">G391</a>, <a href=\"#/G4762\">G4762</a>, <a href=\"#/G654\">G654</a>"}]}